<segment id="1" parent="1001" relname="preparation">Decide Between Religion and Atheism</segment>
<segment id="2" parent="1002" relname="preparation">Beliefs and spirituality are an important part of our lives .</segment>
<segment id="3" parent="1002" relname="joint">Not only to get answers to spiritual questions ,</segment>
<segment id="4" parent="1004" relname="span">but also to identify in a group ,</segment>
<segment id="5" parent="4" relname="purpose">to not feel rejected .</segment>
<segment id="6" parent="1006" relname="span">How to decide</segment>
<segment id="7" parent="6" relname="circumstance">when you do n't know your own beliefs ?</segment>
<segment id="8" parent="1008" relname="preparation">Steps</segment>
<segment id="9" parent="1008" relname="joint">Understanding the Difference Between Religion and Atheism</segment>
<segment id="10" parent="1010" relname="preparation">Know the definitions .</segment>
<segment id="11" parent="1011" relname="span">Most of the time , we look for answers</segment>
<segment id="12" parent="11" relname="manner">without even understanding the question .</segment>
<segment id="13" parent="1013" relname="question">What does it mean to be religious ?</segment>
<segment id="14" parent="1013" relname="joint">To be an atheist ?</segment>
<segment id="15" parent="1016" relname="attribution">You will notice</segment>
<segment id="16" parent="1016" relname="span">that the definitions of these words are n't as clear</segment>
<segment id="17" parent="1017" relname="joint">as they may seem ,</segment>
<segment id="18" parent="1017" relname="joint">and everybody has their own opinion on what they actually mean .</segment>
<segment id="19" parent="1013" relname="joint">Clearly understanding the meanings of these words will help you understand exactly what you are looking for .</segment>
<segment id="20" parent="1020" relname="preparation">Religion :</segment>
<segment id="21" parent="1020" relname="joint">1 .</segment>
<segment id="22" parent="1020" relname="joint">The belief in and worship of a superhuman controlling power , especially a personal God or gods .</segment>
<segment id="23" parent="1020" relname="joint">2 .</segment>
<segment id="24" parent="1020" relname="joint">A particular system of faith and worship .</segment>
<segment id="25" parent="1025" relname="span">3 . A pursuit or interest</segment>
<segment id="26" parent="25" relname="elaboration">to which someone gives supreme importance .</segment>
<segment id="27" parent="1027" relname="span">Religious :</segment>
<segment id="28" parent="27" relname="elaboration">Relating to or believing in a religion .</segment>
<segment id="29" parent="1029" relname="preparation">Atheism :</segment>
<segment id="30" parent="1029" relname="joint">1 .</segment>
<segment id="31" parent="1029" relname="joint">Disbelief or lack of belief in the existence of God or gods .</segment>
<segment id="32" parent="1029" relname="joint">2 .</segment>
<segment id="33" parent="1033" relname="span">Skepticism ,</segment>
<segment id="34" parent="33" relname="elaboration">being unsure about whether or not a god or gods exist .</segment>
<segment id="35" parent="36" relname="preparation">Atheist :</segment>
<segment id="36" parent="1035" relname="span">1 .</segment>
<segment id="37" parent="1037" relname="span">A person</segment>
<segment id="38" parent="37" relname="elaboration">who disbelieves or lacks belief in the existence of God or gods .</segment>
<segment id="39" parent="1036" relname="joint">2 .</segment>
<segment id="40" parent="1040" relname="span">A person</segment>
<segment id="41" parent="40" relname="elaboration">who has no spiritual beliefs .</segment>
<segment id="42" parent="1042" relname="joint">Learn about your subjects .</segment>
<segment id="43" parent="44" relname="concession">Knowing is good ,</segment>
<segment id="44" parent="1044" relname="span">but learning by yourself is better .</segment>
<segment id="45" parent="1046" relname="span">Do research on atheism , on the religion</segment>
<segment id="46" parent="45" relname="elaboration">that interests you ,</segment>
<segment id="47" parent="1046" relname="elaboration">get the definitions clear in your mind .</segment>
<segment id="48" parent="1049" relname="span">Understand what it means to choose a religion ,</segment>
<segment id="49" parent="1050" relname="contrast">to choose to be atheist ,</segment>
<segment id="50" parent="1050" relname="contrast">or even to create your own beliefs .</segment>
<segment id="51" parent="1053" relname="span">Because a religion is made</segment>
<segment id="52" parent="1054" relname="span">to understand things</segment>
<segment id="53" parent="52" relname="elaboration">we ca n't explain better ,</segment>
<segment id="54" parent="1055" relname="same_unit">and</segment>
<segment id="55" parent="56" relname="condition">if you have your own beliefs ,</segment>
<segment id="56" parent="1056" relname="span">you do n't have to pick a religion .</segment>
<segment id="57" parent="1058" relname="span">The research will also help you see all the sides of the medal ,</segment>
<segment id="58" parent="1059" relname="joint">so you do n't have prejudice</segment>
<segment id="59" parent="1059" relname="joint">and you can stay open-minded .</segment>
<segment id="60" parent="1061" relname="preparation">Note your impressions .</segment>
<segment id="61" parent="1061" relname="joint">Get a notebook</segment>
<segment id="62" parent="1064" relname="span">and write everything about religions</segment>
<segment id="63" parent="62" relname="elaboration">that interest you ,</segment>
<segment id="64" parent="1065" relname="span">about being an atheist , about anything</segment>
<segment id="65" parent="64" relname="elaboration">you need .</segment>
<segment id="66" parent="1067" relname="span">That way , you will stay organized .</segment>
<segment id="67" parent="66" relname="elaboration">Learning Your Own Beliefs</segment>
<segment id="68" parent="1068" relname="joint">Do it logically .</segment>
<segment id="69" parent="1071" relname="span">Make a list of pros and cons for each religion</segment>
<segment id="70" parent="69" relname="elaboration">( including atheism )</segment>
<segment id="71" parent="1070" relname="same_unit">in your notebook .</segment>
<segment id="72" parent="1073" relname="span">Write as many arguments</segment>
<segment id="73" parent="72" relname="elaboration">as you can .</segment>
<segment id="74" parent="1075" relname="preparation">Try to see if one religion comes out more frequently ,</segment>
<segment id="75" parent="1077" relname="contrast">has more pros or more cons ,</segment>
<segment id="76" parent="1077" relname="contrast">or has more interesting pros or cons .</segment>
<segment id="77" parent="1078" relname="joint">You can also compare them with categories , such as holidays , restrictions , general beliefs , etc. You can also ask your family and friends what they think ,</segment>
<segment id="78" parent="1079" relname="same_unit">and see</segment>
<segment id="79" parent="80" relname="condition">if they come up with pros or cons</segment>
<segment id="80" parent="1080" relname="span">you did n't think of .</segment>
<segment id="81" parent="1082" relname="span">Basically , try to get a visual representation of what happens in your mind</segment>
<segment id="82" parent="81" relname="purpose">to help you get your ideas clear .</segment>
<segment id="83" parent="1083" relname="joint">Do it spiritually .</segment>
<segment id="84" parent="1085" relname="span">Do meditation</segment>
<segment id="85" parent="1086" relname="joint">before going to bed ,</segment>
<segment id="86" parent="1086" relname="joint">and think about your most profound beliefs .</segment>
<segment id="87" parent="1087" relname="joint">Let your heart guide you .</segment>
<segment id="88" parent="1090" relname="span">Check out videos on YouTube</segment>
<segment id="89" parent="88" relname="elaboration">on how to meditate .</segment>
<segment id="90" parent="1091" relname="same_unit">Plus ,</segment>
<segment id="91" parent="1093" relname="span">if you do it</segment>
<segment id="92" parent="91" relname="circumstance">before going to sleep ,</segment>
<segment id="93" parent="1094" relname="span">your subconscious will work on it during the night</segment>
<segment id="94" parent="93" relname="elaboration">and you will have clearer ideas in the morning .</segment>
<segment id="95" parent="1097" relname="span">The basic concept here is to see</segment>
<segment id="96" parent="95" relname="elaboration">where your mind tells you to go ,</segment>
<segment id="97" parent="1098" relname="joint">to follow your guts</segment>
<segment id="98" parent="1098" relname="joint">and to be open-minded .</segment>
<segment id="99" parent="1099" relname="joint">Try it out !</segment>
<segment id="100" parent="101" relname="condition">If one religion comes out more ,</segment>
<segment id="101" parent="1102" relname="span">always pops up in your mind ,</segment>
<segment id="102" parent="1103" relname="span">or you have any feeling</segment>
<segment id="103" parent="1104" relname="span">this could be what you want ,</segment>
<segment id="104" parent="103" relname="elaboration">try adopting the religion for a year .</segment>
<segment id="105" parent="106" relname="condition">If you think</segment>
<segment id="106" parent="1108" relname="span">this is how you want to live ,</segment>
<segment id="107" parent="108" relname="condition">if you think</segment>
<segment id="108" parent="1109" relname="span">this is what you believe in ,</segment>
<segment id="109" parent="1106" relname="span">then good job !</segment>
<segment id="110" parent="1111" relname="preparation">You have made your choice .</segment>
<segment id="111" parent="112" relname="condition">If not ,</segment>
<segment id="112" parent="1112" relname="span">try again from the beginning .</segment>
<segment id="113" parent="1115" relname="span">Maybe you would prefer a religion</segment>
<segment id="114" parent="113" relname="elaboration">that you did n't yet think of ,</segment>
<segment id="115" parent="1116" relname="joint">or maybe you prefer not knowing</segment>
<segment id="116" parent="1117" relname="span">and simply following the flow of life ,</segment>
<segment id="117" parent="116" relname="elaboration">seeing where it will lead you .</segment>
<segment id="118" parent="1114" relname="motivation">In the end , it all comes to you .</segment>
<segment id="119" parent="1119" relname="preparation">Tips</segment>
<segment id="120" parent="1122" relname="attribution">Always remember</segment>
<segment id="121" parent="1122" relname="same_unit">that you can switch</segment>
<segment id="122" parent="123" relname="condition">if you do n't like the religion</segment>
<segment id="123" parent="1123" relname="span">you chose .</segment>
<segment id="124" parent="1125" relname="span">Talk to people of the religions</segment>
<segment id="125" parent="124" relname="elaboration">that interest you .</segment>
<segment id="126" parent="1127" relname="span">Nothing is better than talking to someone</segment>
<segment id="127" parent="126" relname="elaboration">who lived it</segment>
<segment id="128" parent="1127" relname="purpose">to tell you more about that religion !</segment>
<segment id="129" parent="1119" relname="joint">Warnings</segment>
<segment id="130" parent="1119" relname="joint">Never base your decisions on what others may think of you .</segment>
<segment id="131" parent="1131" relname="span">Never base your decisions on prejudice .</segment>
<segment id="132" parent="131" relname="elaboration">Not being open-minded will hide great opportunities from you .</segment>
<segment id="133" parent="1132" relname="span">Base your decisions mostly on beliefs .</segment>
<segment id="134" parent="1134" relname="condition">If you love your religion</segment>
<segment id="135" parent="1134" relname="span">but do n't believe in the god of that religion ,</segment>
<segment id="136" parent="1135" relname="joint">you should quit</segment>
<segment id="137" parent="1135" relname="joint">and search for what you really believe in .</segment>
